  "extensions": {
    "gnn_section": "ActInfFactorGraph",
    "footer": "Factor Graph Active Inference Model v1 - GNN Representation.\nFactored model enables modality-specific processing.\nBelief propagation on factor graph is more efficient than joint inference.",
